hadiths[1]{hadithnumber,text,grades,reference,international_number,narrator_chain,chapter_intro}:
285,"""I asked Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) about performing the ritual prayer in my home, and performing it in the mosque."" He said: “You may notice how near my home is to the mosque. I prefer praying at home over praying in the mosque, except in the case of a prescribed ritual prayer.”",,,49000,"Abdu’llah ibn Sa'd said:",Chapter 42
